He takahanga i te whakahaerenga ture. Koirā te whakatītina a te tōpūranga o ngā Pirihimana o Aotearoa, ki te noho mauhere tonu a Teina Pora me te kōhurutanga o Susan Burdette. Nā te Perehitini o te tōpūranga o ngā Pirihimana, nā Greg O’Connor te kii, kahore e tino tau nei ngā wairua o ētahi pirihimana ki te noho mauhere tonu a Pora, nō reira, me whakahaere hoki he arotake motuhake.
